\c 108
\s Mwari Mubatsiri wedu ngaarumbidzwe
\d Rwiyo, Pisarema raDhavhidhi.
\p
\v 1 Moyo wangu wakasimba, Mwari; ndichaimba, zvirokwazvo, ndichaimba nziyo dzokurumbidza, nomweya wangu wese.
\p
\v 2 Muka iwe mutengeranwa nembira; ini ndimene ndichamuka mangwanani.
\v 3 Ndichakuvongai Jehovha, pakati pendudzi dzavanhu; ndichakuimbirai nziyo dzokurumbidza pakati pavahedheni.
\v 4 Nokuti tsitsi dzenyu ihuru kumusoro kokudenga-denga, uye zvokwadi yenyu inosvikira kudenga rese.
\v 5 Imwi mukudzwe Mwari, kumusoro kokudenga-denga; kurumbidzwa kwenyu ngakuve kumusoro kwapasi pese.
\v 6 Kuti vadikanwi venyu varwirwe, tiponesei noruoko rwenyu rworudyi, mutipindure.
\p
\v 7 Mwari akataura pautsvene hwake, achiti: Ndichafara kwazvo; ndichaganhura Shekemu, ndichayera mupata weSukoti.
\v 8 Giriyadhi ndeyangu naManase ndeyangu; Efuremuwo inhaviro yomusoro wangu; Judha ndiyo tsvimbo yangu youshe.
\v 9 Moabhu ndiwo mudziyo wangu wokushambidzira; pamusoro peEdhomu ndipo pandichakandira shangu yangu; ndichapururudza nokuda kwaFirisitia.
\p
\v 10 Ndianiko achandiisa muguta rakakombwa namasvingo? Ndianiko achandiperekedza ndiende Edhomu?
\v 11 Hamuna kutirasira here, Mwari, uye hamubudi, Mwari, nehondo dzedu?
\v 12 Tibatsirei pamudzivisi wedu; nokuti kubatsira kwemunhu hakuna maturo.
\v 13 Muna Mwari tichaita noumhare; nokuti ndiye achatsika vadzivisi vedu pasi.